      <title>摩根大通任命里德负责政府和医疗保健业务</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-picks-reed-run-government-healthcare-businesses-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通周二任命柯蒂斯·里德 (Curtis Reed) 为这家美国最大银行的政府银行和医疗保健、高等教育和非营利银行业务主管。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/jpmorgan-picks-reed-run-government-healthcare-businesses-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 12:09:35 GMT</pubDate>
